{"tid":381614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人既人工同購買力係世界上算唔算高?","createTime":"2017-08-31T05:49:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T08:04:57.000Z","uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c75c406f77f0b84be500fef736c9fb5b4ec8695","tid":381614,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:49:29.000Z","msg":"雖然香港薪金中位數好似只係$15,500<br />\n但如果用依幅圖去大概估下平均收入，會發現香港人薪金平均可能有$24,000<br />\n扣埋稅大約係$23,000<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/GNarFTf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FGNarFTf.jpg&h=4f1c85f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n相比起歐洲國家<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_European_countries_by_average_wage\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FList_of_European_countries_by_average_wage&d=EVU0uj8QfCgFZij4OLs6aP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=34d037cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_European_countries_by_average_wage</a><br />\n扣稅後收入: (港元 / 國際元)<br />\n瑞士: $42,000 / $3,990<br />\n冰島: $32,000 / $2,904<br />\n挪威: $31,000 / $3,634<br />\n丹麥: $30,000 / $3,242<br />\n瑞典: $25,000 / $2,989<br />\n芬蘭: $23,000 / $2,704<br />\n德國: $20,000 / $2,914<br />\n法國: $20,000 / $2,767<br />\n英國: $18,000 / $2,522<br />\n<br />\n冇記錯國際元既計法係收入*(購買力平價/國際匯率)<br />\n咁香港國際元係匯率既1.33倍，意味香港人平均收入係$4,122國際元<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而香港物價亦唔係比歐洲高(當然樓價係極高)<br />\n如果只係好單純去計收入，香港人購買力算唔算係世界前列位置?<br />\n仲要講緊依20年黎收入增長少、物價增長高<br />\n咁香港人購買力係10幾20年前咪好鬼高?"},{"pid":"eb23bd7ccd26fc5f6ecd388c4568185f73cc1945","tid":381614,"uid":108606,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:50:42.000Z","msg":"只問一句，單計純收入有乜作用？<br />\n<br />\n你唔計下津巴布韋啲人打一日工有幾錢收？"},{"pid":"59a76c21cca80668e5669fcb03167c0ff9a685ee","tid":381614,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:53:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只問一句，單計純收入有乜作用？<br />\n<br />\n你唔計下津巴布韋啲人打一日工有幾錢收？</blockquote><br />\n所以我咪講「單純收入」<br />\n工時個d香港當然係長，但如果咁計落，香港時薪亦唔係比歐洲低好多"},{"pid":"df862b7e68156b3e7dfbc24e8eff16c1fa69adf3","tid":381614,"uid":45353,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:53:16.000Z","msg":"洗未來錢超越美國"},{"pid":"05cb4eb17cc7aabd95ed1371b7f69cc6dd31d80e","tid":381614,"uid":65554,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:57:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>只問一句，單計純收入有乜作用？<br />\n<br />\n你唔計下津巴布韋啲人打一日工有幾錢收？</blockquote><br />\n所以我咪講「單純收入」<br />\n工時個d香港當然係長，但如果咁計落，香港時薪亦唔係比歐洲低好多</blockquote><br />\n衣食住行<br />\n得食住係必需<br />\n你可以計下其他地區同香港既比例"},{"pid":"76826ddc99051278146d142bcf0ba0dfa3f54b2e","tid":381614,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:58:49.000Z","msg":"諗下都知無可能高過瑞士<br />\n而且你話香港物價平過歐洲，我真係有d 保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfe7ddb9df5d52613794687c3b57de829e30ab4","tid":381614,"uid":9887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:01:47.000Z","msg":"點會用平均數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定會被少數高薪人拉到勁高"},{"pid":"b45d3a6913b8e68feefc10a740027f0bb0e0fc5d","tid":381614,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>只問一句，單計純收入有乜作用？<br />\n<br />\n你唔計下津巴布韋啲人打一日工有幾錢收？</blockquote><br />\n所以我咪講「單純收入」<br />\n工時個d香港當然係長，但如果咁計落，香港時薪亦唔係比歐洲低好多</blockquote><br />\n衣食住行<br />\n得食住係必需<br />\n你可以計下其他地區同香港既比例</blockquote><br />\n依D數據好似好難有"},{"pid":"3c16d36491c0ec9c56896f313160d66f957b6a8c","tid":381614,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:04:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗下都知無可能高過瑞士<br />\n而且你話香港物價平過歐洲，我真係有d 保留<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n當然冇高過瑞士，但國際元既計法的確係咁<br />\n人均GDP(購買力平價)香港都只係低瑞士少少<br />\n物價個度北歐一定高過香港，但西歐個d都唔係低，有d野香港貴有d野個邊貴"},{"pid":"a7e1ed4babf6a43c8e2ef5b50da78241b1cc0833","tid":381614,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:04:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c8bbaf12d44fe049abbe64114a0e30eb887728f3","tid":381614,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:04:45.000Z","msg":"生喺瑞士唔知幾生修到"},{"pid":"fa3171a7a569ee9d0910723e568304ea20ca9b22","tid":381614,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點會用平均數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定會被少數高薪人拉到勁高</blockquote><br />\n因為搵唔到歐洲既中位數數據<br />\n而且幅圖最多都係$60,000或以上，我用左$80,000去計所以未必會因為少數高薪人而拉到勁高"},{"pid":"18c498af73f996ee0ad9c937cd4f2d8b976af854","tid":381614,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:06:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d3980c16facb3070c01c76bf49ece7118b9f921f","tid":381614,"uid":140953,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:10:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>生喺瑞士唔知幾生修到</blockquote><br />\n香港曾幾可時只係差一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係點黎東方瑞士之稱<br />\n香港keep到80年代個個氣場，話唔定係瑞士比人叫西方香港"},{"pid":"2cd46b257ea6651fc56a785da0378877797a3a4b","tid":381614,"uid":115516,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T06:56:03.000Z","msg":"其實香港平均人工係唔差, 尤其去到中產個批, 加上稅率唔高 (利申: 之前有機會去歐洲做野, 但人工真係太低計唔店數冇去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n唔係點會咁多法國佬, 外國鬼來打工<br />\n<br />\n好多中產樓又差唔多供完, 人工又高, 所以先想香港穩定, 話後生搞事<br />\n<br />\n的確呢批人係受惠曬香港之前留落來的優勢, <br />\n<br />\n最9慘一定係而家既後生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4802005cf9cdb509fb94a3da115931470f88cc5","tid":381614,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T07:31:27.000Z","msg":"搵十萬一個月果啲緊係多<br />\n<br />\n搵一萬果啲慘過屎"},{"pid":"f0cd8c08255b5ac61961acac3bfe15c69d6d56ea","tid":381614,"uid":51200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T07:33:27.000Z","msg":"人地計平均數係真係因爲收入叫比較平均，<br />\n香港計既中位收入先fit到香港個case"},{"pid":"0dcda6117c3203184b28f83fe8860c19a771dfbb","tid":381614,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T07:40:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>搵十萬一個月果啲緊係多<br />\n<br />\n搵一萬果啲慘過屎</blockquote><br />\n咁平均數係每人揾55000,幾高薪"},{"pid":"afe30325f533f0c52ed0594d9964b2ac50b5a9b5","tid":381614,"uid":39846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T07:45:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>生喺瑞士唔知幾生修到</blockquote><br />\n香港曾幾可時只係差一步<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係點黎東方瑞士之稱<br />\n香港keep到80年代個個氣場，話唔定係瑞士比人叫西方香港</blockquote><br />\n單以洗黑錢角度黎睇，香港絕對係東方瑞士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"994eaae14cfae3d6120b97cf834945b5b27e9f48","tid":381614,"uid":3117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"賺買力高 人工唔算"},{"pid":"565e6de20b98725e2854baa70ff24572085d4236","tid":381614,"uid":105590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T07:53:13.000Z","msg":"樓價個度可唔可以當香港人購買力低$2000國際元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6949fe1b5529cc0b767c79228ed115f730b29f16","tid":381614,"uid":41116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:00:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓價個度可唔可以當香港人購買力低$2000國際元<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n外國tax burden<br />\n香港rent burden"},{"pid":"381c7177734e0d03d0bcaba0f905010bbe416c1c","tid":381614,"uid":106506,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:04:57.000Z","msg":"0或以上100%<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"